CashUrance UI Overhaul — Winter Chill Theme
Complete visual overhaul of all Flutter screens using the Winter Chill color palette, replacing the current blue/black/white scheme with a cohesive teal-based design system.

Color Palette
Token	Hex	Usage
Ice	#B8E3E9	Light backgrounds, chips, highlights, badges
Sage	#93B1B5	Muted text, borders, disabled states, secondary fills
Teal	#4F7C82	Primary buttons, active indicators, accents
Deep	#0B2E33	Dark backgrounds, text, hero sections, nav bar
