Key Design Principles
Entry screen gets the biggest transformation — logo-centric dark teal splash
Dark panels use #0B2E33 with gradient blends to #4F7C82
Light surfaces use white tinted with ice (#F4FAFB)
Primary actions are #4F7C82 (teal)
Highlights/chips/badges use #B8E3E9 (ice)
Muted/secondary elements use #93B1B5 (sage)
All functional colors (success, warning, error) are retained but slightly adjusted for harmony
